---
title: Tangy Tamarind Chicken with White Rice & Garlicky Green Beans
description: A tangy, buttery pan sauce elevates savory pork chops into this flavor packed crowd-pleaser. Tropical tamarind gives sweet and sour notes to the velvety sauce that cascades onto fluffy white rice. Roasted garlicky green beans make an irresistible side dish, and everything is sprinkled with scallion greens for a fresh, zippy garnish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66b14d8778d91450badf8143-c900a97c.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66b3e80f995e511e4eca9f3e-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Southeast Asia
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tangy-tamarind-chicken-66b3e80f995e511e4eca9f3e
course: main course
